“Fell Asleep At A Rave” album out NOW on YouTube! Link in bio💿!
Back in 2019 my friends at the time kept dragging me to raves & I wasn’t enjoying the music AT ALL! I’d be so bored I’d fall asleep, only to be woken up by other attendees tryna give me water thinking I was on molly or trippin or something lmao. I hated the experience so much that it bothered me that I wasn’t enjoying the music or environment. Immediately I felt like I should make house music & add the elements I felt it was missing in order for me to appreciate it & this is what was created! I finished this album in January 2020 right before Covid hit & never got around to releasing it. Now this sound is so popular in HipHop, but take a listen to see how it’s REALLY supposed to be done😚
